rows.label: tlk401008_msg0001
rows.name:
There are no suspicious movements
within the Superbian army.

rows.label: tlk401008_msg0002
rows.name:
The ones who came to Acedia are the
Emperor's personal Cretas Guard.

rows.label: tlk401008_msg0003
rows.name:
They have all sworn
loyalty to the Emperor.

rows.label: tlk401008_msg0004
rows.name:
If there's any trouble, it would
be from the Invidian side, but...

rows.label: tlk401008_msg0005
rows.name:
It's hard to read their intentions.
I wonder what they're thinking.
